Class ReleaseNotesProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jepria.versionizer.ReleaseNotesProcessor

  • public class ReleaseNotesProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
    Adds particular list of ReleaseNotes into the overview file.

    Invoke #parse(), then addReleaseNotes(boolean), then save(OutputStream)
